</MATH>.
<p>Assuming <MATH>6<G>x</G><SUP>2</SUP> + 4<G>x</G> = <I>m</I><SUP>2</SUP><G>x</G><SUP>2</SUP></MATH>, we have <MATH><G>x</G> = 4 / (<I>m</I><SUP>2</SUP> - 6)</MATH>, and
